ISIKHULU esiphezulu seBhange Ithala, uDkt Thulani Vilakazi, sithi kasikho isidingo sokuthi uhulumeni aqale phansi izinhlelo zokwakha ibhange likahulumeni ngoba Ithala kade laliwenza lowo msebenzi.. UVikalazi usho lokhu emuva kokuthi uMnyango wezeziMali uveze ukuthi kawukaziqedi izinhlelo zokusungula ibhange likahulumeni jikelele yize sekuphele iminyaka ewu-10 uzama ukulakha. “Ithala kade laqala ukusebenza njengebhange likahulumeni, elikudingayo wukwaziwa njengebhange likahulumeni ngokusemthethweni. Asikho isidingo sokuthi uhulumeni aqalaze kwezinye izindawo ngoba Ithala liyawenza lo msebenzi. Siyibhange likahulumeni elinelayisensi yokwenza wonke umsebenzi wamabhange ajwayelekile,” kusho uVilakazi. Uveze ukuthi Ithala likulungele ukuba yibhange likahulumeni nokuguqula impilo yabantu baseNingizimu Afrika, ikakhulukazi labo akade bengakwazi ukufinyelela ezinsizeni zezimali, abale kubo abahlala emakhaya. “Ukusungulwa kwebhange likahulumeni kuzosiza ukuqeda ukungalingani, okwadalwa wubandlululo. Kuzosiza imiphakathi ebingafinyeleli kwezezimali. Ithala lisekwa wuhulumeni waKwaZulu-Natal ukuthi libe yibhange likahulumeni. Lineminyaka ewu-60 likulo mkhakha futhi lingasiza kakhulu ekuqedeni ububha, ukungalingani nokungasebenzi,” kusho uVilakazi. Uphethe ngokuthi ukusiza kwabo imiphakathi yasemakhaya kukhombisa ngokusobala ukuthi bayahambisana nezinhlelo zikahulumeni, zokuthuthukisa umnotho, ngakho uma sebeyibhange likahulumeni akukho okuzobahlula. 